<h1>Dragable and Sortable</h1>

<p class="lead">Add drag and drop to dom nodes and list widgets.</p>

<h2>Dragable</h2>
<p>Use the <code>w-dragable</code> tag to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/Dragable">havok/widget/Dragable</a> to make an element dragable.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-dragable class="label label-info">Drag me!</w-dragable>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dragExample1 %}
<w-dragable class="label label-info">Drag me!</w-dragable>{% endset %}{{dragExample1|e}}
</pre>

<h4>Drag with Grip</h4>
<p>Add a <code>data-havok-grip</code> to indicate a drag grip.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-dragable class="label label-info">Drag me! <i class="fa fa-arrows" data-havok-grip></i></w-dragable>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dragExample2 %}
<w-dragable class="label label-info">Drag me! <i class="fa fa-arrows" data-havok-grip></i></w-dragable>{% endset %}{{dragExample2|e}}
</pre>

<hr class="bs-docs-separator">

<h2>Movable</h2>

<p>Use the <code>w-movable</code> tag to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/Movable">havok/widget/Movable</a> to make an element move and stay when drag is complete.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px">
        <w-movable class="label label-info">Move me!</w-movable>
    </div>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dragExample3 %}
<div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px">
    <w-movable class="label label-info">Move me!</w-movable>
</div>{% endset %}{{dragExample3|e}}
</pre>

<h4>Move with Grip</h4>
<p>Add a <code>data-havok-grip</code> to indicate a move grip.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px">
        <w-movable class="label label-info">Move me! <i class="fa fa-arrows" data-havok-grip></i></w-movable>
    </div>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dragExample4 %}
<div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px">
    <w-movable class="label label-info">Move me! <i class="fa fa-arrows" data-havok-grip></i></w-movable>
</div> {% endset %}{{dragExample4|e}}
</pre>

<h4>Moving with arrow keys</h4>
<p>If a moveable has focus, it can be moved with the arrow keys.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
        <w-movable class="label label-info" tabindex=0>Move me!</w-movable>
    </div>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dragExample5 %}
<div class=well style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
    <w-movable class="label label-info" tabindex=0>Move me!</w-movable>
</div>{% endset %}{{dragExample5|e}}
</pre>

