<h2>Sortable</h2>

<p>Use the <code>sortable</code> attribute on list type widgets to make them sortable via drag and drop. This will mixin the <a href="/api/href/widget/_SortableMixin">havok/widget/_SortableMixin</a> module.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-nav-tab class="nav-stacked" sortable>
        <a href="">ACT</a>
        <a href="">NSW</a>
        <a href="">Vic</a>
        <a href="">Qld</a>
        <a href="">SA</a>
        <a href="">NT</a>
        <a href="">WA</a>
        <a href="">Tas</a>
    </w-nav-tab>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set sortExample1 %}
<w-nav-tab class="nav-stacked" sortable>
    <a href="">ACT</a>
    <a href="">NSW</a>
    <a href="">Vic</a>
    <a href="">Qld</a>
    <a href="">SA</a>
    <a href="">NT</a>
    <a href="">WA</a>
    <a href="">Tas</a>
</w-nav-tab>{% endset %}{{sortExample1|e}}
</pre>

<h3>Sort between lists</h3>

<p>Use the <code>drop-targets</code> attribute to allow sorting between lists.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="row-fluid clearfix">
        <w-nav-tab class="span6 nav-stacked"
            id="leftSortable"
            sortable
            drop-targets="leftSortable rightSortable"
            >
            <li><a>Harry</a></li>
            <li><a>Max</a></li>
            <li><a>Phillip</a></li>
            <li><a>James</a></li>
        </w-nav-tab>
        <w-nav-tab class="span6 nav-stacked"
            id="rightSortable"
            sortable
            drop-targets="leftSortable rightSortable"
            >
            <li><a>Michael</a></li>
            <li><a>Tim</a></li>
            <li><a>Shaun</a></li>
            <li><a>Robert</a></li>
        </w-nav-tab>
    </div>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set sortExample2 %}
<w-nav-tab class="span6 nav-stacked"
    id="leftSortable"
    sortable
    drop-targets="leftSortable rightSortable"
    >
    <li><a>Harry</a></li>
    <li><a>Max</a></li>
    <li><a>Phillip</a></li>
    <li><a>James</a></li>
</w-nav-tab>
<w-nav-tab class="span6 nav-stacked"
    id="rightSortable"
    sortable
    drop-targets="leftSortable rightSortable"
    >
    <li><a>Michael</a></li>
    <li><a>Tim</a></li>
    <li><a>Shaun</a></li>
    <li><a>Robert</a></li>
</w-nav-tab>{% endset %}{{sortExample2|e}}
</pre>

<h3>Horizontal example</h3>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
  <w-nav-pill sortable>
      <a>Tiny</a>
      <a>Small</a>
      <a>Medium</a>
      <a>Big</a>
      <a>Biggest</a>
  </w-nav-pill>
</div>

<h3>Tabs example</h3>

<p>Tabs in a <code>havok/widget/TabContainer</code> are sortable by default.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
  <w-tab-container style="margin-bottom: 18px;">
    <section class="active">
        <header>Section 1</header>
        <p>I'm in Section 1.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <header>Section 2</header>
        <p>Howdy, I'm in Section 2.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <header>Section 3</header>
        <p>What up girl, this is Section 3.</p>
    </section>
  </w-tab-container>
</div>

